            "value": "<p><span><strong>Requirements</strong> You are within melee reach of the opponent you attempt to Feint.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>With a misleading flourish, you leave an opponent unprepared for your real attack. Attempt a Deception check against that opponent’s Perception DC.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> You throw your enemy’s defenses against you entirely off. The target is flat-footed against melee attacks that you attempt against it until the end of your next turn.<br><strong>Success</strong> Your foe is fooled, but only momentarily. The target is flat-footed against the next melee attack that you attempt against it before the end of your current turn.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your feint backfires. You are flat-footed against melee attacks the target attempts against you until the end of your next turn.&nbsp;</p>"
